==English==
====Etymology====
[[corn]] + [[stalk]]
===Noun===

{{en-noun}}
#{{botany}} The tough, fibrous stalk of a [[corn]] ([[maize]]) plant, often ground for [[silage]] after harvest.
#{{botany}} A single specimen of a corn plant once past the [[seedling]] stage and which may, at maturity, bear multiple [[ear]]s of corn.